{"title":"Combined feed","url":"https://Vinnl.github.io/feeds/all.xml","elements":[{"title":"Julius Prott (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that international opera star <b><a href=\"/wiki/Julius_Prott\" title=\"Julius Prott\">Julius Prott</a></b> <i>(pictured)</i> was also a horticulturalist who was acclaimed for his cultivation of roses?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Julius_Prott","retrieved":1779180167526},{"title":"plateau vole (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that the <b><a href=\"/wiki/Plateau_vole\" title=\"Plateau vole\">plateau vole</a></b> handles <a href=\"/wiki/Hypoxia_(environmental)\" title=\"Hypoxia (environmental)\">hypoxia</a> at high altitudes by producing more <a href=\"/wiki/Hemoglobin\" title=\"Hemoglobin\">hemoglobin</a> and metabolizing glucose?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Plateau_vole","retrieved":1779180167528},{"title":"Aileen Allen (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that Olympic diver and coach <b><a href=\"/wiki/Aileen_Allen\" title=\"Aileen Allen\">Aileen Allen</a></b> was also an actress in <a href=\"/wiki/Silent_film\" title=\"Silent film\">silent films</a>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aileen_Allen","retrieved":1779180167530},{"title":"a New York City warehouse (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that a restaurant in <b><a href=\"/wiki/Fleming_Smith_Warehouse\" title=\"Fleming Smith Warehouse\">a New York City warehouse</a></b> converted a loading dock into a terrace?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fleming_Smith_Warehouse","retrieved":1779180167530},{"title":"2024 Chilean census (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that the <b><a href=\"/wiki/2024_Chilean_census\" title=\"2024 Chilean census\">2024 Chilean census</a></b> was delayed twice by a total of nearly two years?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2024_Chilean_census","retrieved":1779180167533},{"title":"Nathan Farb (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Nathan_Farb\" title=\"Nathan Farb\">Nathan Farb</a></b> carried his large-format 8×10 Deardorff view camera into the backcountry of the <a href=\"/wiki/Adirondack_Mountains\" title=\"Adirondack Mountains\">Adirondack Mountains</a> to capture scenery far from the most-visited areas?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nathan_Farb","retrieved":1779180167535},{"title":"O Menino e o Vento (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that the Brazilian film <i><b><a href=\"/wiki/O_Menino_e_o_Vento\" title=\"O Menino e o Vento\">O Menino e o Vento</a></b></i> was rejected from the 1967 <a href=\"/wiki/Venice_Film_Festival\" title=\"Venice Film Festival\">Venice Film Festival</a> for being \"old and unimportant\" and \"full of useless ideas\"?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/O_Menino_e_o_Vento","retrieved":1779180167536},{"title":"his inauguration in 2019 (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that Ukrainian president <a href=\"/wiki/Volodymyr_Zelenskyy\" title=\"Volodymyr Zelenskyy\">Volodymyr Zelenskyy</a> jumped to kiss his best friend on the head as he walked to <b><a href=\"/wiki/Inauguration_of_Volodymyr_Zelenskyy\" title=\"Inauguration of Volodymyr Zelenskyy\">his inauguration in 2019</a></b>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Inauguration_of_Volodymyr_Zelenskyy","retrieved":1779180167538},{"title":"Alan J. Southward (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that marine ecologist <b><a href=\"/wiki/Alan_J._Southward\" title=\"Alan J. Southward\">Alan J. Southward</a></b> almost never got sea-sick—because he was deaf?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alan_J._Southward","retrieved":1779180167541},{"title":"Destination of the Month (Wikivoyage recommendations)","contents":"<span class=\"mw-empty-elt\" about=\"#mwt8\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\" id=\"mwIg\" data-mw=\"{&quot;parts&quot;:[{&quot;template&quot;:{&quot;target&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;banner&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;./Template:Banner&quot;},&quot;params&quot;:{&quot;direction